{%- comment -%}
  LE FIGUE — "By Appointment" page.
  Step 1 of the booking flow: guest picks an appointment type and reserves a
  time. SINCE 2026-07-05 the booking engine is SESAMI: the old demo day/time
  picker (client-side mock, could double-book) was retired per the CEO dev
  guide — "Reserve the Suite" now routes to /products/house-appointment, where
  Sesami's Book Now calendar shows LIVE availability (NoHo Atelier / Virtual
  resources, capacity 1/slot) and the checkout reserves the slot atomically.
  The chosen type (Gift Edit / Styling Session / Personal Shopping) rides
  along as a ?type= param for future use (Klaviyo survey link phase).
  The pre-appointment survey (/pages/appointment-survey → Basin → concierge@)
  is step 3, sent after booking (manual/Klaviyo; it accepts type/ref params).
  Custom & Bespoke has its own page (/pages/custom-bespoke) + its own Sesami
  service (/products/custom-bespoke-consultation). CSS namespaced .lf-*.
{%- endcomment -%}

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable-dynamic-subset.css">

<div class="lf-page lf-appt">
  <div class="lf-ap-hero">
    <div class="lf-eyebrow lf-eyebrow--gold">By Appointment · The Suite</div>
    <h1 class="lf-display lf-ap-h1">A room kept for you.</h1>
    <p>LE FIGUE is a styling studio before it is a store, not a floor to sell from. We sit with you in The Suite, a private room set aside for one guest at a time. Come to choose a gift, to learn your stack, or simply to shop the way you'd want to.</p>
    <p class="lf-fine"><span class="lf-ast">*</span> Every appointment is offered with our compliments.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="lf-band">
    <div class="lf-concepts">
      <div class="lf-concept">
        <div class="lf-viz"><span class="lf-eyebrow lf-eyebrow--accent">The Gift Edit</span><span class="lf-vt">Read between<br>the lines</span></div>
        <div class="lf-c-eye">The Gift Edit <span class="lf-c-dur">· 15–30 min</span></div>
        <h3 class="lf-display">The right gift, every time.</h3>
        <p>A partner, a mother, a friend, the thank-you you've put off for too long. Bring three things: who they are, the day it's for, and what you'd like to spend. From years of watching how people actually wear what we carry, a curator chooses with you, the piece they'd never buy themselves.</p>
        <span class="lf-lk" data-lf-reserve="Gift Edit">Reserve the Gift Edit →</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lf-concept">
        <div class="lf-viz"><span class="lf-eyebrow lf-eyebrow--accent">The Styling Session</span><span class="lf-vt">Bring the<br>question</span></div>
        <div class="lf-c-eye">The Styling Session <span class="lf-c-dur">· 30–45 min</span></div>
        <h3 class="lf-display">Stacks, layers, daily.</h3>
        <p>Bring the question, any question. Ten fingers you'd like to read as one. Necklaces meant to fall in layers. Earrings chosen for where you're actually pierced, lobe to helix. We pair what you own with what's new, and find the one piece you'll never take off.</p>
        <span class="lf-lk" data-lf-reserve="Styling Session">Reserve the Styling Session →</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lf-concept">
        <div class="lf-viz"><span class="lf-eyebrow lf-eyebrow--accent">Personal Shopping</span><span class="lf-vt">Already<br>chosen</span></div>
        <div class="lf-c-eye">Personal Shopping <span class="lf-c-dur">· about 60 min</span></div>
        <h3 class="lf-display">For the regulars.</h3>
        <p>For the ones who already know the names. The new arrivals first, then what pairs with the pieces already in your collection. An hour in a private room, no rush, no crowd. New to the house? Just as welcome, we'll start at the beginning.</p>
        <span class="lf-lk" data-lf-reserve="Personal Shopping">Reserve Personal Shopping →</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lf-band lf-line-top" id="lf-book">
    <div class="lf-appt-grid">
      <div class="lf-appt-copy">
        <div class="lf-eyebrow lf-eyebrow--gold">Reserve · The Suite</div>
        <h2 class="lf-display">Keep a time.</h2>
        <p>Select the kind of appointment, then choose your room and hour on the next page — the calendar shows live availability for the NoHo atelier and for virtual sittings. The Concierge will confirm your sitting within 24 hours.</p>
        <div class="lf-appt-types" data-lf-group="type">
          <button type="button" class="lf-chip lf-on" data-value="Gift Edit">Gift Edit</button>
          <button type="button" class="lf-chip" data-value="Styling Session">Styling Session</button>
          <button type="button" class="lf-chip" data-value="Personal Shopping">Personal Shopping</button>
        </div>
        <div class="lf-appt-note">Complimentary · One on one · The Suite</div>
      </div>

      <div class="lf-appt-card">
        <div class="lf-booking" id="lf-booking-form">
          <div class="lf-bk-head"><span>Reserve a time</span><span class="lf-bk-mon">Live availability</span></div>

          <div class="lf-bk-steps">
            <div class="lf-step"><span class="lf-step-n">1</span><span>Choose the <b>NoHo Atelier</b> or a <b>Virtual</b> sitting, and pick your hour on the live calendar.</span></div>
            <div class="lf-step"><span class="lf-step-n">2</span><span>Confirm — the hour is held for you alone. Every appointment is complimentary.</span></div>
            <div class="lf-step"><span class="lf-step-n">3</span><span>A short note follows, so your curator can prepare your edit before you arrive.</span></div>
          </div>

          <a class="lf-bk-cta" data-lf-cta href="/products/house-appointment">Reserve the Suite →</a>
          <div class="lf-bk-foot">Real-time calendar on the next page · we confirm within 24 hours.</div>
          <div class="lf-bk-alt">Beginning a custom piece? <a href="/pages/custom-bespoke">For Custom &amp; Bespoke →</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lf-band lf-line-top lf-who">
    <div class="lf-band-head"><div class="lf-eyebrow lf-eyebrow--gold">Who You'll Sit With</div><h2 class="lf-display">A quiet sitting, guided with care.</h2></div>
    <p>Your appointment is guided by people who live closely with jewelry — designers, buyers, and curators who understand proportion, material, craftsmanship, and the quiet details that make a piece feel right. We look at how you dress, how you move, what you already love, and what you may not have found yet. We are not here to persuade. We are here to sit beside you, with care.</p>
    <div class="lf-q lf-display">Come in. We've been keeping something for you.</div>
    <div class="lf-attr">Curator, LE FIGUE</div>
    <p class="lf-fine"><span class="lf-ast">*</span> Every appointment is offered with our compliments.</p>
  </section>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .lf-page {
    --lf-ink:#2a2622; --lf-ink-soft:#6b635a; --lf-line:#e3dccf; --lf-line-soft:#efe9dd;
    --lf-cream:#faf7f1; --lf-cream-deep:#f3ede1; --lf-accent:#8a7250; --lf-gold:#b8975f; --lf-paper:#fdfbf6;
    background:var(--lf-cream); color:var(--lf-ink);
    font-family:'Pretendard Variable','Pretendard',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
    font-weight:400; line-height:1.7; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  .lf-page *{ box-sizing:border-box; }
  .lf-display{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; }
  .lf-eyebrow{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:15px; }
  .lf-eyebrow--gold{ color:var(--lf-gold); }
  .lf-eyebrow--accent{ color:var(--lf-accent); }

  .lf-band{ max-width:1280px; margin:0 auto; padding:60px 30px; }
  .lf-line-top{ border-top:1px solid var(--lf-line); }
  .lf-band-head{ text-align:center; margin-bottom:40px; }
  .lf-band-head h2{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-weight:500; font-size:clamp(28px,3.6vw,40px); margin-top:6px; }

  .lf-ap-hero{ max-width:1280px; margin:0 auto; padding:88px 30px 18px; }
  .lf-ap-hero .lf-eyebrow{ font-size:16px; }
  .lf-ap-h1{ font-weight:500; font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,64px); line-height:1.04; letter-spacing:-.01em; margin:14px 0 16px; }
  .lf-ap-hero p{ font-size:15.5px; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); max-width:540px; }
  .lf-fine{ margin-top:18px; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:13px; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); }
  .lf-ast{ color:var(--lf-gold); }

  .lf-viz{ position:relative; width:100%; border:1px solid var(--lf-line);
    background:radial-gradient(120% 120% at 75% 12%, #efe8db 0%, #e6dac6 55%, #dccdb4 100%);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:flex-end; padding:20px; overflow:hidden; }
  .lf-viz::before{ content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.18) 0 1px, transparent 1px 9px); opacity:.5; }
  .lf-viz .lf-eyebrow{ position:relative; font-size:13px; }
  .lf-vt{ position:relative; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:22px; line-height:1.15; color:var(--lf-ink); margin-top:4px; }

  .lf-lk{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:15px; color:var(--lf-ink);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--lf-accent); padding-bottom:3px; cursor:pointer; transition:color .18s; }
  .lf-lk:hover{ color:var(--lf-accent); }

  .lf-concepts{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:30px; }
  .lf-concept{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
  .lf-concept .lf-lk{ margin-top:auto; align-self:flex-start; }
  .lf-concept .lf-viz{ min-height:280px; }
  .lf-c-eye{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:var(--lf-gold); font-size:14px; margin:16px 0 4px; }
  .lf-c-dur{ color:var(--lf-ink-soft); }
  .lf-concept h3{ font-weight:500; font-size:25px; line-height:1.12; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .lf-concept p{ font-size:14px; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:16px; }

  .lf-appt-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 420px; gap:54px; align-items:center; }
  .lf-appt-copy .lf-eyebrow{ font-size:15px; }
  .lf-appt-copy h2{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-weight:500; font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,46px); margin:6px 0 14px; }
  .lf-appt-copy p{ font-size:15px; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); max-width:440px; }
  .lf-appt-types{ display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:24px; }
  .lf-chip{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:14px; padding:9px 18px;
    border:1px solid var(--lf-line); background:none; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); cursor:pointer; border-radius:30px; transition:.18s; }
  .lf-chip:hover{ border-color:var(--lf-accent); color:var(--lf-ink); }
  .lf-chip.lf-on{ background:var(--lf-accent); color:#f7f1e6; border-color:var(--lf-accent); }
  .lf-appt-note{ margin-top:20px; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--lf-gold); }

  .lf-appt-card{ background:var(--lf-paper); border:1px solid var(--lf-line); padding:26px 26px 24px;
    box-shadow:0 26px 50px -34px rgba(42,38,34,.4); }
  .lf-bk-head{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline;
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:18px; padding-bottom:16px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--lf-line-soft); }
  .lf-bk-mon{ font-style:italic; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); font-size:14px; }

  .lf-bk-steps{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px; padding:20px 0 4px; }
  .lf-step{ display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:flex-start; font-size:13px; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); line-height:1.65; }
  .lf-step b{ color:var(--lf-ink); font-weight:500; }
  .lf-step-n{ flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; border:1px solid var(--lf-accent); border-radius:50%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
    font-style:italic; font-size:12px; color:var(--lf-accent); margin-top:2px; }

  .lf-bk-cta{ display:block; width:100%; text-align:center; margin-top:18px; background:var(--lf-ink);
    color:#f4eee2; border:none; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:16px;
    padding:14px; cursor:pointer; transition:.2s; text-decoration:none; }
  .lf-bk-cta:hover{ background:var(--lf-accent); }
  .lf-bk-foot{ margin-top:14px; text-align:center; font-size:11.5px; color:var(--lf-ink-soft);
    font-style:italic; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; }
  .lf-bk-alt{ margin-top:16px; padding-top:14px; border-top:1px solid var(--lf-line-soft); text-align:center;
    font-size:12.5px; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); }
  .lf-bk-alt a{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:var(--lf-accent);
    text-decoration:none; border-bottom:1px solid var(--lf-accent); padding-bottom:1px; }
  .lf-bk-alt a:hover{ color:var(--lf-ink); border-color:var(--lf-ink); }

  .lf-who{ text-align:center; }
  .lf-who p{ max-width:640px; margin:0 auto; color:var(--lf-ink-soft); font-size:15.5px; line-height:2; }
  .lf-q{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:24px; color:var(--lf-ink); margin-top:30px; }
  .lf-attr{ font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:14px; color:var(--lf-gold); margin-top:8px; letter-spacing:.06em; }
  .lf-who .lf-fine{ margin-top:24px; }

  @media(max-width:900px){
    .lf-concepts{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:40px; }
    .lf-appt-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:30px; }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% javascript %}
  (function () {
    var root = document.querySelector('.lf-appt');
    if (!root) return;

    var SERVICE_URL = '/products/house-appointment';
    var cta = root.querySelector('[data-lf-cta]');

    // keep the CTA href carrying the selected type (?type=) for the
    // post-booking survey phase (Klaviyo link build) — harmless on the
    // product page itself.
    function currentType() {
      var on = root.querySelector('.lf-appt-types .lf-chip.lf-on');
      return on ? on.getAttribute('data-value') : '';
    }
    function syncCta() {
      if (!cta) return;
      var t = currentType();
      cta.setAttribute('href', SERVICE_URL + (t ? ('?type=' + encodeURIComponent(t)) : ''));
    }

    var typeGroup = root.querySelector('[data-lf-group="type"]');
    if (typeGroup) {
      typeGroup.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
        var btn = e.target.closest('button');
        if (!btn || !typeGroup.contains(btn)) return;
        typeGroup.querySelectorAll('button').forEach(function (b) { b.classList.remove('lf-on'); });
        btn.classList.add('lf-on');
        syncCta();
      });
    }

    // concept-card links select their type and scroll to the reserve band
    root.querySelectorAll('[data-lf-reserve]').forEach(function (lk) {
      lk.addEventListener('click', function () {
        var type = lk.getAttribute('data-lf-reserve');
        root.querySelectorAll('.lf-appt-types .lf-chip').forEach(function (c) {
          c.classList.toggle('lf-on', c.getAttribute('data-value') === type);
        });
        syncCta();
        var book = document.getElementById('lf-book');
        if (book) book.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
      });
    });

    syncCta();
  })();
{% endjavascript %}

